{
  "stem": "3100.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember, I had the [INAUDIBLE] Erev Shavuos living on Stockton Street, which was before they came out also like Shabbos before, and they gave me maftir.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When I said the maftir, they asked me if I would daven Musaf.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I davened Musaf for them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that summer-- that summer-- of course, before, I got-- I, I got the two shteles in 1951.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In 1950, I had two shteles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In 1951, I davened at the Fallsberg--",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the Pines Hotel.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then for Yom Kippur, they weren't open.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was hired to daven in the-- in Flatbush, in a congregation [INAUDIBLE], which means for the martyrs, the shul for the--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- I didn't even get paid for it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was an honor for me to be able to daven in a shul with this rabbi who was also a Holocaust survivor.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I davened Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But on that July before High Holidays, I got a call in the morning.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, I came from Washington, and we need a chazzan, a cantor for High Holidays.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Would you accept a shtele?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, who told you about it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, my mother goes to the shul, and she lives a block away from you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she heard you in that shul on Stockton Street, and she told me that you are good chazzan.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Therefore, I want to come over and talk to you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he came over-- by the name of Scotty Feldman-- and he came over, and he engaged me right away for High Holidays to go to Maryland, College Park, in Washington.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got paid $800 for a job which I never thought was a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It's not a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
